# --- Basemap source ---------------------------------------------------------
# Phase 1 renders a MapLibre basemap. Two ways to supply it:
#
# 1. A full MapLibre vector style URL (preferred — matches the README's
#    OSM vector-tile direction, e.g. a self-hosted PMTiles style or a hosted
#    style endpoint). If set, this wins.
VITE_MAP_STYLE_URL=
#
# 2. If no style URL is given, the app falls back to a built-in raster OSM
#    style so the map renders out of the box for local dev. The raster tile
#    template below can be overridden. (OSM tile usage policy applies — use a
#    proper vector source before shipping.)
VITE_RASTER_TILE_URL=https://tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png
VITE_RASTER_ATTRIBUTION=© OpenStreetMap contributors
